data.title: Major League Baseball Players Association opens an office in Arizona
data.meta_description: SCOTTSDALE, Ariz., Feb. 27 – The Major League Baseball Players Association today announced the opening of its Arizona office. The new space will provide a central location to expand the current support given to Players before, during and after their careers.  “Our membership is highly concentrated in Arizona, both at the Major and Minor League levels, which makes it an ideal location for us to establish a presence,” MLBPA Executive Director Tony Clark said. “The office here will allow us to impr
